    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with this absolute beauty, and let me tell you, it is in incredible shape! It\u2019s been babied since day one\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a single scratch or dent to be found, and the interior is just as spotless. I\u2019m looking for someone who will appreciate a ride this perfect. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
